Carrières-sous-Poissy

Carrières-sous-Poissy is a city in Île-de-France, in France.

GPS Coordinates of Carrières-sous-Poissy, Île-de-France, France

Carrières-sous-Poissy is located on the latitude of 48.94952 and longitude of 2.04068 and has a geohash of u09qqqvzx7ck.

Cities and Towns near Carrières-sous-Poissy

The nearest significant population center from Carrières-sous-Poissy is Bû in Centre-Val de Loire, France, located 43 kilometers or 26 miles ↙ SW of the city. Other locations in close proximity include Anet (Centre-Val de Loire, France) located 45 km (28 mi) ↙ SW and Droue-sur-Drouette (Centre-Val de Loire, France) located 46 km (28 mi) ↓ S of Carrières-sous-Poissy.
